==Translingual==

===Etymology 1===
From the {{der|mul|ett|-}} letter {{m|ett|êåÄ}}, from the {{der|mul|grc|-}} letter {{m|grc|Œë||alpha}}, derived from the {{der|mul|phn|-}} letter {{m|phn|ê§Ä||[[aleph]]}}, from the {{der|mul|egy|-}} hieroglyph {{m|egy|ìÉæ}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|mul|/a/|qq=most languages}}

